  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize move_to_marker upon marker_seen; stay in marker_approach until marker_close.",
    "Commit to forward or rotation actions to avoid dithering and ensure progress.",
    "After each forward commit or recovery, insert a scan (full_rotate) to search for the marker.",
    "Use recovery_reverse after obstacle_front before resuming exploration.",
    "Alternate between forward_commit and scan_full to balance exploration and marker search.",
    "Use rotate_commit_cw/ccw to escape side obstacles, never both in the same state.",
    "Upon marker_close, stop to complete the task safely.",
    "All states handle all uncontrollable events to ensure robustness."
